if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d79c57e8d0b95c7d39c597d0283f3e2246fc56","tid":904844,"uid":193893,"like":123,"dislike":0,"score":123,"quote":{"pid":"0bf19f45b588ddcddf9f95550109b25ac6caa41a","tid":904844,"uid":199902,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"諗唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快啲推到三頁開估<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打交足戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4b464028bb40f62eef98a089f82a58f0141cca","tid":904844,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":37,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"古梵文裏，觀音原名Ａvalokitesvara是男性名詞。而在原始佛教經典中，也一再稱觀音為〔勇猛丈夫〕或〔善男子〕。<br />\n<br />\n《華嚴經》裏善財童子五十三參，，到了普陀洛迦山參擇觀音時記載：〔見岩石林中金剛石上，有勇猛丈夫觀自在，與諸大菩薩圍繞說法。〕<br />\n<br />\n《悲華經》裏提到觀音是轉輪聖王的王子的時說：〔善男子，今當字汝，為觀世音。汝行菩薩道行時，已有百千億那由他眾生，得離苦惱。〕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n●隨機化現的觀音性別<br />\n然而，在《法華經&middot;普門品》以及《楞嚴經》中都提到觀音具有三十二或三十三變化身的願力，這些變化身裏有一些女身，例如《大佛頂首楞嚴經》說：〔觀世音尊者自佛言，若有女人好學出家，我於彼前是（現）比丘尼身，女王身，國王夫人身，命婦身，大家童女身，而為說法。〕告訴我們勇猛丈夫觀世音為了弘法的方便，可以變換性別和各種身份。"},{"pid":"3d403286598321f7ef6d8e6cb08e63d1a460c1e4","tid":904844,"uid":190771,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"你呢個時候出post<br />\n都係想人答嗰個答案姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af92610036ab69183e34cf4e7b725214b01a434a","tid":904844,"uid":193893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eb4b464028bb40f62eef98a089f82a58f0141cca","tid":904844,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":37,"score":-35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"古梵文裏，觀音原名Ａvalokitesvara是男性名詞。而在原始佛教經典中，也一再稱觀音為〔勇猛丈夫〕或〔善男子〕。<br />\n<br />\n《華嚴經》裏善財童子五十三參，，到了普陀洛迦山參擇觀音時記載：〔見岩石林中金剛石上，有勇猛丈夫觀自在，與諸大菩薩圍繞說法。〕<br />\n<br />\n《悲華經》裏提到觀音是轉輪聖王的王子的時說：〔善男子，今當字汝，為觀世音。汝行菩薩道行時，已有百千億那由他眾生，得離苦惱。〕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n●隨機化現的觀音性別<br />\n然而，在《法華經&middot;普門品》以及《楞嚴經》中都提到觀音具有三十二或三十三變化身的願力，這些變化身裏有一些女身，例如《大佛頂首楞嚴經》說：〔觀世音尊者自佛言，若有女人好學出家，我於彼前是（現）比丘尼身，女王身，國王夫人身，命婦身，大家童女身，而為說法。〕告訴我們勇猛丈夫觀世音為了弘法的方便，可以變換性別和各種身份。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:11:52.000Z","msg":"阿彌陀佛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e651ad44dbed91013e0fcefa6d0c95fa00160736","tid":904844,"uid":193893,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"3d403286598321f7ef6d8e6cb08e63d1a460c1e4","tid":904844,"uid":190771,"like":67,"dislike":1,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:09:39.000Z","msg":"你呢個時候出post<br />\n都係想人答嗰個答案姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:12:56.000Z","msg":"終於比你識穿左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實呢個係笑話post，1q題只係掛羊頭賣狗肉既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"878b00e105a8a22b8ffa6fffd7156ffbed9fe284","tid":904844,"uid":170229,"like":63,"dislike":1,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"肯認俾人秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正皮"},{"pid":"84c12d34a1c088df19dfb49f0a0db3340d19d8cd","tid":904844,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e651ad44dbed91013e0fcefa6d0c95fa00160736","tid":904844,"uid":193893,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":